From a0070a3a10343491c67b77ce9f3ff7573796b727 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: scwhine <scwhine@fractal-north>
Date: Mon, 18 May 2026 15:34:03 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] winewayland: bind zwp_linux_dmabuf_v1; add dmabuf surface
 attach, cross-process IPC, SNI systray

- Makefile.in: add linux-dmabuf XML, wayland_dmabuf.c, wayland_systray.c, -ldbus-1
- wayland.c: bind zwp_linux_dmabuf_v1 (version 3) in registry handler
- waylanddrv.h: add zwp_linux_dmabuf_v1 to struct wayland; declare new helpers
- wayland_dmabuf.c: wayland_surface_attach_dmabuf (wl_buffer from fd),
  wayland_share_dmabuf_for_hwnd / wayland_get_dmabuf_for_hwnd (wineserver IPC)
- server/protocol.def: add share_dmabuf_fd + get_dmabuf_fd requests
- server/wayland_dmabuf.c: wineserver handlers (fd broker per HWND)
- window.c: WAYLAND_UpdateLayeredWindow tries dmabuf path then wl_shm fallback
- wayland_systray.c: pSystrayDockInit/Insert/Clear/Remove via libdbus SNI
- waylanddrv_main.c: register all new driver hooks

Signed-off-by: scwhine <scwhine@fractal-north>

